						<p class="txt mt8">[환급계좌]<br>
							대구은행 <em class="number">504101120661</em>
						</p>
						<div class="radiobox">
							<ul class="inline_rchk">
								<li>
									<input type="radio" name="r0311" value="" id="r0311" class="rchk" aria-hidden="true" title="동의함 체크">
									<label for="r0311" class="rchk-label" role="radio" aria-checked="false"><span>동의함</span></label>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>

						<h2>이용약관 동의</h2>
						<p class="icon_bullet mt0">아래 약관에 동의하셔야 시설대여(리스) 상품이용이 가능합니다.</a></p>
						<!-- 이용약관 전체동의// -->
						<div class="form_box mt40">
							<div class="checkbox">
								<input type="checkbox" id="ch30" name="ch30" class="chk" aria-hidden="false" title="전체동의">
								<label for="ch30" class="label font22" role="checkbox">전체 동의</label>
								<span class="img">
									<a href="#"><img src="/static/web/img/ico_openwindow.png" class="open_img" alt="동의서 내용보기"></a>
								</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<p class="line"></p>
						<div class="form_box">
							<div class="checkbox">
								<input type="checkbox" id="ch031" name="ch031" class="chk chk_1" aria-hidden="false" title="전자금융거래 기본약관">
